    "notes": "v2.0: removed paywalled sources (Bloomberg, Economist, Sifted) and EU-heavy 'The Local' country feeds. Added APAC/China/India/LATAM/MEA regional coverage. GDELT covers gaps where dedicated English sources are sparse. 'region' = where the source is based/focused; 'region_tags' = Microsoft regions the content is most relevant to."
